title: For Sale:  Genuine Short Barrel Colt 2nd Gen Dragoon
postcontent: TRADES POSSIBLE. You've never seen a Dragoon like this, and likely never will again. This is a 2nd generation Colt percussion Second Model Dragoon pistol, still one of the most powerful handguns ever made. Has custom shorty barrel 4.5 inches long. 28xxx serial range from the 1980's. This is the only one of these you have ever seen. Has been fired but is in excellent condituion. Not just a chopped off barrel but complete with custom reduced ramrod assembly and beautiful contouring as found on certain 19th century conversions.  And importantly, unlike many second generation Colts that do not work properly when they are put into use thirty-five years after they were made, this one functions perfectly. It can take several hours just to tune up a second generation cap and ball Colt when it comes out of the box because Colt intended these guns to be 'collector items' and not shooters. Additionally, it takes many hours and special tooling to do the custom reduction and contouring to the barrel and front end. This pistol has an extremely smooth action and works perfectly. I have fired it, but as with all black powder pistols I offer, there is no warranty of any kind, express or implied, as to the use or safety of this or any other percussion pistol regardless of age. A beautiful piece and something no one else you know has! Please email any questions. Trades possible!
